    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033770/extras/71974a658156eda7a17f77305602ef0b.poster.avif?t=1754848857\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033770/extras/71974a658156eda7a17f77305602ef0b.webm?t=1754848857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033770/extras/71974a658156eda7a17f77305602ef0b.mp4?t=1754848857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>《第七圣歌》是一款受PS2狩猎游戏和《启示录》启发的恐怖游戏。</strong><br><br>深入古老洞穴那阴森的走廊。遇见一个神秘的披风人物，他的脸被一副不祥的面具遮掩。倾听并相信他所传述的，那位带来第七圣歌哭号之人的话语。<br><br><i>一个可以在一小时内完成的短篇恐怖体验。</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033770/extras/752fb4c1f0344e0dcf01712f01b6dc05.poster.avif?t=1754848857\" width=598 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033770/extras/752fb4c1f0344e0dcf01712f01b6dc05.webm?t=1754848857\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033770/extras/752fb4c1f0344e0dcf01712f01b6dc05.mp4?t=1754848857\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点</h2><strong>沉浸式故事：</strong> 带有分支对话选项的序章，将你引入游戏的黑暗宗教背景。<br><strong>Lo-Fi视觉效果：</strong> 受PS2时代游戏启发的复古画面。<br><strong>探索：</strong> 探索一片被雪覆盖的沼泽、森林和遗忘时代的废墟。<br><strong>真实的狩猎玩法：</strong> 使用望远镜观察动物，藏身在瞭望台中，追踪你在雪地里的猎物。<br><strong>紧张的音效：</strong> 渐渐枯萎的沼泽中，令人毛骨悚然的音景将你深深地拉入悬念之中。<br><strong>神秘人物：</strong> 令人难以置信的超自然存在视觉效果。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2>当你聆听第七圣歌的话语时，你发现自己身处一片浓密的冰封沼泽，手持步枪。你必须穿越这片寒冷而令人恐惧的景观，找到你被指派要猎杀的麋鹿。在追踪麋鹿的过程中，他将你引向沼泽的深处，夜幕降临，你发现了被遗忘信仰的遗物。",
